==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Toxine
<hw>Tox"ine</hw> }</mhw> <pr>(?)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <grk>toxiko`n</grk>. See <er>Toxic</er>. ]</ety>
<def>A poisonous product formed by an organism, such as a pathogenic
bacterium, a plant or an animal, usually having a high molecular weight,
often a protein or a polysaccharide, but occasionally a low-molecular
weight agent such as <stype>tetrodotoxin</stype>.</def></p>

<p><ent>Toxiphobia</ent>⟦br⟧
